   - [ ] 资源不存在\n111: \n112: #### 5.3 Build 函数测试\n113: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxObject()`\n114:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox 对象\n115:   - [ ] 随机后缀生成\n116:   - [ ] 标签和注解正确复制\n117:   - [ ] 容器配置正确转换（command, args, env）\n118:   - [ ] env 的不同类型处理（value, valueFrom）\n119: - [ ] 测试 `BuildSandboxClaimObject()`\n120:   - [ ] 成功构建 claim 对象\n121:   - [ ] 标签正确设置\n122: - [ ] 测试 `BuildCodeInterpreterSandbox()`\n123:   - [ ] 成功构建 sandbox\n124:   - [ ] 容器配置正确\n125: \n126: #### 5.4 Pod IP 解析测试\n127: - [ ] 测试 `resolvePodIP()`\n128:   - [ ] pod 直接通过名称找到\n129:   - [ ] pod 未运行状态\n130:   - [ ] pod 无 IP\n131:   - [ ] 通过 label selector 查找\n132:   - [ ] 通过 owner reference 匹配\n133:   - [ ] pod 不存在\n134: \n135: #### 5.5 EntryPoint 构建测试\n136: - [ ] 测试 `BuildEntryPoints()` - 入口点正确构建\n137: \n138: #### 5.6 CreateSandbox 测试\n139: - [ ] 测试 `CreateSandbox()`\n140:   - [ ] 成功创建 sandbox\n141:   - [ ] 创建超时回滚\n142:   - [ ] pod 等待超时\n143:   - [ ] warm pool 模式\n144: \n145: #### 5.7 回滚测试\n146: - [ ] 测试 `rollback()` - sandbox 删除回滚\n147: \n148: ### 6. Reconciler 测试\n149: \n150: #### 6.1 Manager 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/manager_test.go) **[待创建]**\n151: - [ ] 测试 `DefaultReconcilerConfig()`\n152: - [ ] 测试 `NewControllerManager()`\n153:   - [ ] 成功创建\n154:   - [ ] 客户端配置（QPS, Burst）\n155:   - [ ] context 初始化\n156: - [ ] 测试 `AddReconciler()`\n157: - [ ] 测试 `SetupEventRecorder()`\n158: - [ ] 测试 `Start()`\n159: - [ ] 测试 `Shutdown()`\n160: - [ ] 测试 getter 方法\n161: - [ ] 测试 `CalculateBackoff()` - 退避算法\n162: - [ ] 测试 `MapObjectReference()` - 对象引用映射\n163: \n164: #### 6.2 AgentRuntime Reconciler 测试 (pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/agentruntime_reconciler_test.go) **[待创建]**\n165: - [ ] 测试 `NewAgentRuntimeReconciler()`\n166: - [ ] 测试 `Run()`\n167: - [ ] 测试 `processNextWorkItem()`\n168: - [ ] 测试 `Reconcile()`\n169:   - [ ] AgentRuntime 不存在\n170:   - [ ] 删除时间戳设置（资源删除中）\n171:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建成功\n172:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（可重试错误）\n173:   - [ ] sandbox pod 创建失败（不可重试错误）\n174:   - [ ] 状态更新成功\n175:   - [ ] 状态更新失败\n176: - [ ] 测